</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>《Fire Emblem 無雙，風花雪月》6 月 24 日發售，將繼承前版故事角色</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/12/nintendo-switch-fire-emblem-warriors-three-hopes/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=nintendo-switch-fire-emblem-warriors-three-hopes</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 12 Feb 2022 05:45:42 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[遊戲情報]]></category><category><![CDATA[Fire Emblem 無雙，風花雪月]]></category><category><![CDATA[Switch]]></category><category><![CDATA[任天堂]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1085622</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>任天堂，早前舉辦網上直播發佈會 「Nintendo Direct 2022.2.10」，宣佈將推出改編自《聖火 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">任天堂，早前舉辦網上直播發佈會 「Nintendo Direct 2022.2.10」，宣佈將推出改編自《聖火降魔錄，風花雪月》的 Switch 遊戲《Fire Emblem 無雙，風花雪月（ファイアーエムブレム無双，風花雪月）》發售日期定在 2022 年 6 月 24 日。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1085624" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/A7DAEBCC-18F3-4827-897E-5DD2F46B478D-694x419.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="419" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/A7DAEBCC-18F3-4827-897E-5DD2F46B478D-694x419.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/A7DAEBCC-18F3-4827-897E-5DD2F46B478D-1280x773.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/A7DAEBCC-18F3-4827-897E-5DD2F46B478D-768x464.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/A7DAEBCC-18F3-4827-897E-5DD2F46B478D-1536x927.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/A7DAEBCC-18F3-4827-897E-5DD2F46B478D-2048x1237.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/A7DAEBCC-18F3-4827-897E-5DD2F46B478D.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1085625" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/3D5352FE-A963-4BD0-A5D2-1951EC3C242B-694x384.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="384" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/3D5352FE-A963-4BD0-A5D2-1951EC3C242B-694x384.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/3D5352FE-A963-4BD0-A5D2-1951EC3C242B-1280x708.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/3D5352FE-A963-4BD0-A5D2-1951EC3C242B-768x425.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/3D5352FE-A963-4BD0-A5D2-1951EC3C242B-1536x850.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/3D5352FE-A963-4BD0-A5D2-1951EC3C242B-2048x1133.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/3D5352FE-A963-4BD0-A5D2-1951EC3C242B.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>（圖片來源：YouTube）</p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">《Fire Emblem 無雙，風花雪月》繼承 2019 年《風花雪月》的背景故事及角色，融合動作及模擬要素的「無雙」玩法，編織出被阿德剌斯忒亞帝國、法嘉斯神聖王國以及雷斯塔諸侯同盟三大勢力所統治的芙朵拉大地風貌。玩家可操作自己的角色以開拓道路，並向同伴傳達指令攻擊敵人。戰場上的戰況會實時變動，體驗結合動作和模擬的戰鬥；玩家亦可根據地圖上的形勢判斷「行軍」方向，與角色進行深入對話交流。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1085626" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/843E5E2B-1761-42EA-BD8F-D8C8307D7D93-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/843E5E2B-1761-42EA-BD8F-D8C8307D7D93-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/843E5E2B-1761-42EA-BD8F-D8C8307D7D93-1280x720.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/843E5E2B-1761-42EA-BD8F-D8C8307D7D93-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/843E5E2B-1761-42EA-BD8F-D8C8307D7D93-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/843E5E2B-1761-42EA-BD8F-D8C8307D7D93-2048x1152.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/843E5E2B-1761-42EA-BD8F-D8C8307D7D93.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-imag